The paper discusses the security protocol for IoT/5G devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed protocol involves key management and authentication, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the deployment of the protocol in the LTE architecture, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
